      <title>土耳其将恢复可再生能源拍卖以促进投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/turkey-to-resume-renewable-energy-auctions-to-boost-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情官员透露，土耳其计划到 2035 年每年至少提供 2,000 兆瓦的新增可再生能源容量，以加速该领域的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/turkey-to-resume-renewable-energy-auctions-to-boost-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 09:12:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美联储降息预期消退，美元有望创下 2022 年以来最佳涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/dollar-set-for-best-run-of-gains-since-2022-as-fed-cut-bets-fade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国经济的复苏迫使交易员再次重新考虑对美联储更积极降息的押注，美元有望创下两年多来的最佳涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/dollar-set-for-best-run-of-gains-since-2022-as-fed-cut-bets-fade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 09:11:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马士基、赫伯罗特计划 2025 年启航南非航线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/maersk-hapag-lloyd-plan-to-sail-south-of-africa-into-2025-m21n7zwo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两家集装箱运输巨头马士基航运和赫伯罗特航运开始进行船舶共享合作，并计划从非洲南部开始合作航行，这表明他们预计红海在 2025 年之前仍然不安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/maersk-hapag-lloyd-plan-to-sail-south-of-africa-into-2025-m21n7zwo</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 09:04:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长卡济米尔在关键数据不明的情况下对 10 月降息持怀疑态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/ecb-s-kazimir-not-convinced-on-october-cut-without-key-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员彼得·卡西米尔表示，他并不像一些媒体报道的那样确定下周会降息——这表明今年最后一次会议可能是再次降息的更合适时机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/ecb-s-kazimir-not-convinced-on-october-cut-without-key-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 09:02:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管经济不景气，德国公共部门员工仍希望加薪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/german-public-sector-staff-want-pay-boost-despite-economic-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国威尔第工会主席弗兰克·沃内克表示，德国公共部门工人不会仅仅因为今年经济将再次陷入萎缩而降低工资要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/german-public-sector-staff-want-pay-boost-despite-economic-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 09:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富时罗素指数：希腊股市瞄准发达市场地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/greek-stocks-on-path-to-developed-market-upgrade-by-ftse-russell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着希腊逐渐摆脱长达十年的债务危机并恢复正常，希腊股市距离再次加入发达市场行列又近了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/greek-stocks-on-path-to-developed-market-upgrade-by-ftse-russell</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 08:28:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称大众银行正考虑收购已故创始人家族在 LPI 的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/public-bank-is-said-to-consider-buying-late-founder-s-family-stake-in-lpi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，大众银行有限公司 (Public Bank Bhd.) 正在考虑收购其已故创始人郑鸿标 (Teh Hong Piow) 家族在 Lonpac Insurance Bhd. 所有者的股份。]]></description>
